Finance Agreement :2-I-A3 | Description :RD shall maintain the FPU to assist RD in Project-related procurement, monitoring andevaluation and project reporting. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :2-I-A6 | Description :By not later than February 28, 2010 the RD shall recruit a financial auditor in terms ofreference and conditions satisfactory to the Bank | Due Date :28-Feb-2010

Finance Agreement :2-I-C-2a | Description :RD shall ensure that the provisions of the respective EMP for the road section areadequately included in the proposed contract(s) for said works | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :2-I-C-2b | Description :RD shall ensure owners and users of the land implemented are fully compensated inaccordance with the provisions of the RAP for the road section | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :2-I-C-3a | Description :RD shall, in accordance with the EIA and RPF, prepare and submit to the Bank an EMP andRAP satisfactory to the Bank | Due Date :31-Mar-2010

Finance Agreement :2-I-C-3b | Description :RD shall ensure that EMP provisions are adequately included in the proposed contract(s);and owners and users of the land are fullycompensated in accordance with the provision of RAP | Due Date :31-Dec-2011
